00:25:37.582 --> 00:25:47.058
It requires the highest calling on our lives from us because sometimes justice means that we forgive those who have persecuted us.

00:25:48.034 --> 00:25:55.902
Sometimes justice means that we ask not for the death penalty when someone has murdered a loved one.

00:25:58.304 --> 00:26:10.477
Sometimes justice means that we have to sacrifice for someone else to have just a little bit of what we have.

00:26:10.497 --> 00:26:15.602
But in God's economy, justice is not optional.

00:26:17.474 --> 00:26:27.385
It is required, and we must find a way to turn this world right side up.

00:26:30.408 --> 00:26:34.953
We can do that through our legislative government.

00:26:35.214 --> 00:26:36.836
We can do that through our churches.

00:26:36.936 --> 00:26:46.226
We can do it all by ourselves by righting wrongs in our world by giving to organizations that help right wrong, especially your church.

00:26:48.866 --> 00:26:49.687
seek the Lord.

00:26:51.770 --> 00:26:54.873
So that God might give you an opportunity to do justice this week.

00:26:56.315 --> 00:27:01.662
And while you're at it, help us prepare for the friends at the front door on February 3rd.

00:27:02.082 --> 00:27:11.934
We need toiletry kits and food and prayer cards and all kinds of things that you can provide so that we might do justice in this world.

00:27:12.815 --> 00:27:15.058
It will take all of us.

00:27:16.130 --> 00:27:21.038
And yet God has already given us everything that we need.

00:27:23.302 --> 00:27:24.383
So let us pray together.

00:27:25.645 --> 00:27:27.789
Oh, dear Heavenly Father, thank you for justice.

00:27:28.330 --> 00:27:35.922
Thank you for designing this world in such a way that you allow us to do justice to love mercy and to walk humbly with you.

00:27:36.578 --> 00:27:40.745
Lord, we pray for every single person that is under the sound of my voice today.

00:27:41.165 --> 00:27:55.588
We pray for them, O God, as you lead us in the path of justice, you lead us in the path of righteousness, O God, knowing that justice and righteousness are the same thing and are intertwined together, Lord.

00:27:57.792 --> 00:28:04.402
Give us a clean heart and renew a right spirit with us.

00:28:06.370 --> 00:28:27.055
Lord, if there's anyone who needs to say yes to you today, who has heard the good news of justice and wants to be a part of this community of faith, Lord, allow them to email me today or in the days ahead or to put something in the chat so that we might be in touch and welcome you to into the family of God.

00:28:27.115 --> 00:28:31.701
And Lord, help us to act.

00:28:33.103 --> 00:28:35.986
Help us not to just stay on our knees.

00:28:36.066 --> 00:28:38.395
but get up and do the work.

00:28:39.981 --> 00:28:43.956
In the name of the Father, the Son and the Holy Spirit, we pray.

00:28:45.220 --> 00:28:45.682
Amen.
